<headline>Special Weather Statement issued February 28 at 4:00AM EST  by NWS Blacksburg</headline>
<description>Patchy dense fog has developed across portions of the Virginia
Piedmont this morning. Visibilities may drop below a quarter mile
at times. Use caution and leave plenty of room between cars if
driving. Fog should dissipate this morning as westerly winds
develop.</description>
